{"tid":2445231,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美國抗中女將任副國務卿　承諾制裁迫害香港的官員","createTime":"2021-03-13T12:44:59.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-13T14:04:31.000Z","uid":227801,"like":23,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"ea571cf7144fd730bd5d024ddc4807a5eb7564c5","tid":2445231,"uid":227801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T12:44:59.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20210313/2UQQCSHWBRATZI6ZD7KFH5XK5Q/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210313%2F2UQQCSHWBRATZI6ZD7KFH5XK5Q%2F&d=Jsj5S9oV5Ro3bsckYFcJfBjXlokmAnOoGQHL1SEg040%3D&h=0e017ea5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210313%2F2UQQCSHWBRATZI6ZD7KFH5XK5Q%2F&h=5fa5aa27\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20210313/2UQQCSHWBRATZI6ZD7KFH5XK5Q/</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/resizer/9zEwECrWwQdr4uuNApgv1xnyTlY=/499x332/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/T2A6P72KTVEXDGHCBXXK3WWW2E.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F9zEwECrWwQdr4uuNApgv1xnyTlY%3D%2F499x332%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FT2A6P72KTVEXDGHCBXXK3WWW2E.jpg&h=36845eed&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n美國參議院外交委員會前天通過任命外交老將雪蔓（Wendy Sherman）出任副國務卿。雪蔓認為美國須與中國競爭，並應在南海與人權上對抗中國，承諾制裁打壓香港民主人權的中國官員。她也曾訪問台灣，與蔡英文總統會面。<br />\n<br />\n參議院外委會在審議任命時，雖有部分議員因雪蔓曾是2015年伊朗核子協議主要談判代表而反對她出任副國務卿，但委員會最終仍以14比8的票數通過提名。雪蔓的任命將送交參議院全院審議，若獲得過半數參議員支持便通過。<br />\n雪蔓在人事聽證會上說明，共和、民主兩黨都認同中國是美國一大挑戰，美國須與之競爭並勝出，在網路安全、商業機密、南海與人權等問題上面臨中國挑戰。她承諾若獲得任命，將來會對打壓香港民主人權的中國官員有效實施制裁。<br />\n<br />\n現年71歲的雪蔓外交資歷豐富，曾在歐巴馬任內擔任國務次卿，在柯林頓政府也曾任北韓政策協調官員。她在2016年卸下國務次卿職務後訪台，出席「台美日暨亞太區域夥伴安全對話研討會」，並與總統蔡英文會面。■國際中心"},{"pid":"2a5d215a0baef35eef008edbc562a860ec3b5768","tid":2445231,"uid":15010,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"202